{"type": "article", "id": 25495, "title": "几何织物", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162640SkgRy1mWrhwAuN4L.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套纺织物来自美国平面设计师 Sara Berks 的品牌 Minna Goods，包括地毯、枕套、毛巾、毯子等。几何图案相互拼接搭配柔和的色彩，整体风格很居家但拥有活泼的元素，既能适应环境又不会显得单调。设计师和墨西哥、危地马拉的艺术家一起合作使用传统的手工艺区去制作。而 Minna 这个名字源于她的祖母，在 1940 年从德国到美国时走丢了，设计师称她喜欢这个有点怀旧和叛逆的故事。<a href=\"http://www.minna-goods.com/collections/all\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162637LYf5SkBQ29uFnidK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162637qd3tm7sGAp6FVbZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162638RC3MbX0nVky56cIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162638fOH8APd5uZsvYcN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162639YuXFtgCB7i0DUs34.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}